        {
            "title": "比特幣險守八萬美元  ETF全線挫",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比特幣下挫，今早險守八萬美元大關，以太幣也捱沽，曾低見1991.195美元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"比特幣 / 虛擬資產 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250227_FI_source-ap_Crypto_Bitcoin.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"比特幣 / 虛擬資產 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250227_FI_source-ap_Crypto_Bitcoin.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">比特幣 / 虛擬資產 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華夏比特幣(03042)急跌8.17%，低見10元，現跌6.98%，報10.13元；南方比特幣(03066)急跌6.77%，報28.66元；博時比特幣(03008)瀉7.11%，報6.34%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">博時HashKey以太幣ETF(03009)跌5.93%，報1.59%；華夏以太幣ETF(03046)降5.85%，報4.94元；南方以太幣(03068)跌5.77%，報10.12元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比特幣今早一度挫3.7%，低見80019美元，最新造81862美元，跌1.5%；以太幣一度跌穿兩千美元關，最低見過1991.195美元，挫2.5%，最新造2046美元，跌0.03%。</p>\n</div>",
